19:20.250 --> 19:22.290
I don't want them to look at that the same way.

410
19:22.290 --> 19:23.910
<v ->Yeah, you wanna make sure you have</v>

411
19:23.910 --> 19:25.080
that trust across the board.

412
19:25.080 --> 19:26.310
<v ->Exactly.</v>

413
19:26.310 --> 19:28.950
<v ->So one of the biggest shifts in the audio landscape</v>

414
19:28.950 --> 19:33.210
