418
19:42.420 --> 19:44.250
Can you talk a little bit about your perspectives

419
19:44.250 --> 19:46.320
on this, video, social, other platforms,

420
19:46.320 --> 19:47.250
how you leverage them?

421
19:47.250 --> 19:50.349
<v ->Yeah, I mean, when I created the podcast, like I said,</v>

