21:17.820 --> 21:19.350
and saying, "Hey, you didn't know about us,

462
21:19.350 --> 21:20.910
but come over here, we've got something else."

463
21:20.910 --> 21:22.950
And I think that that's the way that

464
21:22.950 --> 21:24.693
you leverage that appropriately.

