21:25.800 --> 21:28.020
And you, I mean, you've made a name for yourself in audio

466
21:28.020 --> 21:31.440
as well in the car specifically.

467
21:31.440 --> 21:33.240
What do you think about the new landscape?

468
21:33.240 --> 21:38.100
Like how are you really tackling changes in consumption?

